        public java.lang.String differentiateString​(java.lang.String function)
        Performs differentiation calculations on a specified function.
        Parameters:
        function - A math function given in string form. Preconditions: A polynomial +/- sin or cos function. Coefficients included for polynomials but not for sine and cosine.
        Returns:
        The derivative of the function in string form.
